{"title":"推开春天的门","authors":["商泽军"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":4,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"推开春天的门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商泽军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把春天的门推开一条缝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里面就有鸟的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滑翔而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看着鸟儿在树上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比照着蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从一朵花向另一朵花上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滑翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把春的门再打大一点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的气息拥抱着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就如一个孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在春的怀抱中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我推的是春天的门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个天真烂漫孩子的门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她要到乡村去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到城里去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不只属于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪朵花儿和哪段流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天是属于这个季节的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于这个季节的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个星辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天和黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她属于在路上行走的马蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和马蹄下的花香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她属于流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和流水身上佩带的铃铛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把春天的门推开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人说：余下的时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要跟着春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在她的身后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记录她走过的足迹……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}